  },
  "comment": " Shared types for guidance — FileType, MemberType, Member, Stage, QueryResult, etc.\n\n ## Memory Ownership\n\n   - GuidanceDoc: Owns members slice and module-level comment; call deinit() to release.\n   - Stage: Content and source strings are allocator-owned; free with freeStage() or\n     freeStages() (frees the entire []Stage slice and each stage's content/source).\n   - Member, Skill, Param, Meta: Contain borrowed string slices from their parent\n     GuidanceDoc or source JSON — do not free individually; valid until parent deinit.\n   - FileType, MemberType, StageKind, QueryResult, FileMatch, GuidanceInfo: Value types\n     (no heap allocation).\n   - jsonifyMember / jsonifyGuidanceDoc: Return owned ArrayList(u8); caller owns.",
  "used_by": ["src/guidance/ast_parser.zig", "src/guidance/comments/core.zig", "src/guidance/comments/core_tests.zig", "src/guidance/comments/header.zig", "src/guidance/comments/header_tests.zig", "src/guidance/comments/inserter.zig", "src/guidance/comments/sync.zig", "src/guidance/comments/sync_tests.zig", "src/guidance/core/excerpt.zig", "src/guidance/core/format.zig", "src/guidance/core/metadata.zig", "src/guidance/document_indexer.zig", "src/guidance/document_indexer_tests.zig", "src/guidance/main.zig", "src/guidance/pattern.zig", "src/guidance/plugin.zig", "src/guidance/plugins/markdown_plugin.zig", "src/guidance/plugins/markdown_plugin_tests.zig", "src/guidance/plugins/treesitter_extractor.zig", "src/guidance/plugins/treesitter_plugin.zig", "src/guidance/plugins/zig_plugin.zig", "src/guidance/query/llm_filter.zig", "src/guidance/query/llm_filter_batch.zig", "src/guidance/query/strategy.zig", "src/guidance/query/synthesize.zig", "src/guidance/query_engine.zig", "src/guidance/schema_validator.zig", "src/guidance/skeleton.zig", "src/guidance/stage_builder.zig", "src/guidance/stage_builder_tests.zig", "src/guidance/staged.zig", "src/guidance/staged_tests.zig", "src/guidance/sync.zig", "src/guidance/sync/gen_files.zig", "src/guidance/sync/json_store.zig", "src/guidance/sync/json_writer.zig", "src/guidance/sync/line_verify.zig", "src/guidance/sync/line_verify_tests.zig", "src/guidance/sync_engine.zig", "src/guidance/types_tests.zig"],
